{"1":{"w":[{"b":"0.15","h":"0.33","c":"إِنَّآ","d":"innā","e":"Indeed, We","i":"اِنَّاۤ"},{"b":"2.1","h":"1.55","c":"أَعۡطَيۡنَٰكَ","d":"aʿṭaynāka","e":"have given you","i":"اَعۡطَيۡنٰكَ"},{"b":"4.9","h":"5.66","c":"ٱلۡكَوۡثَرَ","d":"l-kawthara","e":"Al-Kauthar","i":"الۡكَوۡثَرَؕ"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, We have granted you, [O Muhammad], al-Kawthar."}},"2":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.03","c":"فَصَلِّ","d":"faṣalli","e":"So pray","i":"فَصَلِّ"},{"b":"0.92","h":"1.34","c":"لِرَبِّكَ","d":"lirabbika","e":"to your Lord","i":"لِرَبِّكَ"},{"b":"1.9","h":"3.19","c":"وَٱنۡحَرۡ","d":"wa-in'ḥar","e":"and sacrifice","i":"وَانۡحَرۡؕ"}],"a":{"g":"So pray to your Lord and sacrifice [to Him alone]."}},"3":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.03","c":"إِنَّ","d":"inna","e":"Indeed","i":"اِنَّ"},{"b":"1.6","h":"1.4","c":"شَانِئَكَ","d":"shāni-aka","e":"your enemy","i":"شَانِئَكَ"},{"b":"2.7","h":"3.23","c":"هُوَ","d":"huwa","e":"he (is)","i":"هُوَ"},{"b":"3.2","h":"4.07","c":"ٱلۡأَبۡتَرُ","d":"l-abtaru","e":"the one cut off","i":"الۡاَبۡتَرُ"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, your enemy is the one cut off."}}}